name: Boring Inu
description: Boring Inu is the cutest dog created based on Elon's GIGA factory. Boring Inu was loved by Elon and his Boring company. All the fund of this contribution will go to Liquidity Pool and the community will decide what's next of Boring Inu. And the partnership of Boring Inu Rocket Club is going to bring some lovers of Boring Inu to this community.
